title: Journey.Into.an.Invisible.War.PDTV.x265-MVGroup
description:
The story of how Israeli settlements continue to spread into Palestinian territory despite international opposition.

French producer and reporter Paul Moriera travels through the West Bank to meet Palestinians and Israeli settlers. In Hebron, Moriera sees how the old Arab city is gradually being overwhelmed by Israeli incomers, whose security forces are imposing a bizarre street-by-street apartheid on the Palestinians who have always lived there. Moriera encounters the sometimes startling intolerance of their ultra-orthodox communities.
